      <title>贝利警告市场不要对英国央行投票分歧做出鸽派反应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/bailey-cautions-markets-on-dovish-reaction-to-boe-vote-split</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国央行行长安德鲁贝利警告市场不要过多解读本月政策制定者的投票情况，此前一位官员的意外转变促使投资者加大对进一步降息的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/bailey-cautions-markets-on-dovish-reaction-to-boe-vote-split</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Pimco 总裁将高等级债券和 MBS 视为 2025 年的最佳投资选择</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/principal-pimco-bet-on-debt-from-riskier-high-grade-companies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2024 年表现最好的美国蓝筹债券基金坚持其制胜策略：投资风险较高的蓝筹公司的债务，以及能够应对经济动荡的公司的债务——并避开对利率风险敏感的公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/principal-pimco-bet-on-debt-from-riskier-high-grade-companies</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 15:50:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Lightspeed 股价暴跌，因选择保持上市并回购股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/lightspeed-tumbles-as-it-opts-to-stay-public-buy-back-stock</link>
      <description><![CDATA[支付处理软件制造商 Lightspeed Commerce Inc. 表示，计划继续以上市公司的身份运营，并寻求进行小规模收购。开盘后，该公司股价在多伦多下跌 18% —— 创下一年来最大跌幅 —— 随后收复失地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/lightspeed-tumbles-as-it-opts-to-stay-public-buy-back-stock</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 14:43:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
