      <title>市场增加对英国央行宽松政策的押注，无视央行的利率评论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/traders-boost-boe-easing-bets-favor-three-more-cuts-in-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在政策制定者一如预期地将借贷成本降低四分之一个百分点并且其中两位投票支持更大幅度降息之后，交易员们加大了对英国央行今年进一步降息的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/traders-boost-boe-easing-bets-favor-three-more-cuts-in-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 12:09:51 GMT</pubDate>
